      "releaseNotes": "We made a few things easier this update. Tap **+ Add to Shelf** and items now appear instantly — with a one-tap **UNDO** if you change your mind. Your **Flux micro-apps** also remember their last result — reopening one picks up right where you left off. And if you've fallen behind on *Shelf* updates, we'll give you a gentle nudge at launch so you don't miss out on the latest improvements.\n\nWe never stop making bug fixes and small improvements to the app. See anything weird? Reach out to us directly in the app — we'll be on it!",
